= SDL_JoystickOpen =
Use this function to open a joystick for use.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_Joystick* SDL_JoystickOpen(int device_index)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''device_index'''
|the index of the joystick to query
|}

== Return Value ==
A joystick identifier, or NULL if an error occurred.

